<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>Welcome to Freedom Podcasting — your show is ready to launch.</p>

<p>Here are three things to do first:</p>

<p>
  <strong>1. Create your podcast</strong><br>
  Add your show title, artwork, and description so your feed is ready to submit to Apple Podcasts and Spotify.
</p>

<p>
  <strong>2. Publish your first episode</strong><br>
  Upload your audio file, write your show notes, and hit Publish. Your RSS feed updates automatically.
</p>

<p>
  <strong>3. Submit to the directories</strong><br>
  Copy your RSS feed URL from the podcast settings page and submit it to Apple Podcasts, Spotify, and any other directories you want.
</p>

<p><a href="<%= @dashboard_url %>" class="btn">Go to your dashboard</a></p>

<p style="color:#888888;font-size:13px;">Questions? Reply to this email — we read every one.</p>
